41
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:14,800
<b><font color="#ffff00">Apa kamu lelah?</font></b>

42
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:16,920
<b><font color="#ffff00">Aku tidak melakukan apapun.</font></b>

43
