<b><font color="#ffff00">Tentu.</font></b>

128
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,320
<b><font color="#ffff00">Tapi,</font></b>

129
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:19,240
<b><font color="#ffff00">jangan membuat wanita tua ini kesulitan.</font></b>

130
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,640
<b><font color="#ffff00">Meskipun Anda sudah tua,</font></b>

131
