<b><font color="#ffff00">Ada.</font></b>

136
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:41,840
<b><font color="#ffff00">Apa itu?</font></b>

137
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:45,680
<b><font color="#ffff00">Mie Pedas Delapan Harta Karun.</font></b>

138
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:49,800
<b><font color="#ffff00">Baiklah.</font></b>

139
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,840
<b><font color="#ffff00">Aku akan membelinya untukmu sekarang.</font></b>

140
