158
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:24,000
<b><font color="#ffff00">Kita harus pergi.</font></b>

159
00:15:55,400 --> 00:15:56,880
<b><font color="#ffff00">Aku akan kembali ke Shanghai bersama Shancai.</font></b>

160
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:00,240
<b><font color="#ffff00">Apa maksudmu?</font></b>

161
